# Frontend Environment Variables (Optional - kept for future use)
# 
# NOTE: The frontend now uses relative API paths (/api) instead of hardcoded URLs.
# The Nginx reverse proxy handles routing of /api requests to the backend service.
#
# This file is for reference and future extensibility.
# No build-time environment variables are required for the frontend build.

# Example: If you need to override the frontend in the future
# VITE_APP_NAME=DAMS
# VITE_LOG_LEVEL=info
